# /apg-risky-plan

## Purpose

Plan before changing Tier 2-3 areas in {{projectName}}.

## Applies to

- Dangerous modules: {{inlineList risks.dangerousModules}}
- Legacy modules: {{inlineList risks.legacyModules}}
- API/status/schema/frontend/external contracts.
- Human-review areas: {{inlineList risks.humanReviewRequired}}

## Steps

1. Read all `CLAUDE*.md` files.
2. Trace affected call chains and contracts.
3. Identify verification commands.
4. Produce an implementation plan and wait for approval before editing.

## Stop conditions

Do not implement before approval.
